{
  "texts": [
    "This entailed a qualitative aggregation of the numerous topics identified by BERTopic into a smaller number of general topics (i.e. themes).",
    "This process drew from an iterative qualitative refinement approach inspired by grounded theory principles 66.",
    "Given the unsupervised nature of the BERTopic model, it was vital to conduct a thorough evaluation of the interpretability of the generated topics.",
    "We engaged in reviewing the keywords provided for each topic (i.e.",
    "Interpretability evaluation)."
  ]
}